in examining Max's allergy.

569
00:31:12,139 --> 00:31:15,309
Can classical music
written by a bunch of straight,

570
00:31:15,342 --> 00:31:18,646
Austro-German, churchgoing
white guys exalt us,

571
00:31:18,680 --> 00:31:21,148
individually
as-as well as collectively,

