conformity.

605
00:33:31,278 --> 00:33:33,280
I guess Edgard Varèse is okay.

606
00:33:33,313 --> 00:33:35,249
I mean, I like "Arcana," anyway.

607
00:33:35,282 --> 00:33:38,285
